            <title>[LU-8648] Remove all reference to Sun Inc in our source code.</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8648</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently in our source code we have a URL for the GPL license pointing to a site at Sun Inc that no longer exist. Also often given is the Sun snail mail address that also no longer exist. We need to use the proper GPL URL and remove the Sun Inc addresses in our code.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
